overview: Alan wants to sign up for the army, but not as a solider like Nick. He wants to be the entertainment, and when Nick questions what kind of entertainment, Alan shows him what he has to offer. Alex is a hard working fireman who goes to see Travis for a massage. Travis is so turned on by his fire fighting outfit that he is quick to take Alex’s uniform off and really get to work. Johan comes home to Justin sulking on the couch. Justin is sad that Johan will be off flying planes for a while, so they decide to make the best of their time left together. Paul comes home from work and sees Dee taking a nap. He is so turned on by Dee’s uniform that he wakes him up in the sexiest way possible.
title: Men in Uniform 5
